creator: Deep Link Lab
descriptionHtml:
2Apps Space is a new parallel space & multiple accounts app, with the whole new ui interface and multi-app-engine, allow you clone apps and login to multiple accounts at the same time, on any mobile phone.

- One tap to clone app
- One tap to start clone apps
- Login second accounts on the clone app
- Use two accounts of one apps, one phone
- Manage clone app with app info page
- Privacy lock, protect your privacy
- Usage summary
descriptionShort: 2 Clone apps space,for login dual whatsapp accounts at the same time.
